{"tid":678247,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大佬「肥威」門生傳欠四百萬街數","createTime":"2018-05-26T02:38:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-26T04:01:57.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3cb8d6cbea9773db76d214ee5a0a9421d54b9f54","tid":678247,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T02:38:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180526/20401806\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180526%2F20401806&d=FvKVFpRkfxLCbEuMlWiRZf6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=9f6c8f47\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180526%2F20401806&h=12b7cc8a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180526/20401806</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年05月26日 <br />\n<br />\n大佬「肥威」門生傳欠四百萬街數<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180526/large/26la3p06.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180526%2Flarge%2F26la3p06.jpg&h=53b9b5ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■遇襲水房小頭目手腳受傷，送院敷治。姜偉康攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】黑幫和勝和惡鬥水房血案，消息指雙方爭執緣於一筆約400萬元街數。活躍深水埗及西九龍的勝和小頭目「肥仔亮」經營一間財務公司，近期指水房姓黃叫Ken的「小頭目」欠下400萬元巨債，多次追討無果，有人查悉Ken前晚會在西貢出現，於是部署刀手向他施下馬再追數，豈料刀手出師未捷反被打傷。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，肥仔亮是勝和元老「魚欄標」門生，原本在深水埗魚欄搵食，其後勢力擴展至旺角「夜場勝地」新興大廈，他近年行為出位，2014年旺角佔領區內爆發黑幫反佔中大混戰，他被指是負責「吹雞」幫會分子之一，近年則進軍財務借貸活動。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n前年涉「良景之亂」<br />\n<br />\nKen的大佬是「水房」前坐館「肥威」，昨日是肥威49歲生日，前晚在西貢一酒樓設宴慶生，約30多名門生出席。<br />\n<br />\n肥威姓何，2011年前獲水房元老「高佬發」欽點做坐館，負責揸數，操控旺角區麻雀館、夜總會和指壓場，管理幫會收入來源，但引來另一幫中大佬「業仔」不滿，自行推另一門生「子鳳」當坐館，自此水房鬧出雙坐館，內訌不斷升級。<br />\n<br />\n2013年2月，肥威在尖沙嘴與家人食開年飯後離開時，遭30名同門敵對派系黑漢伏擊。肥威登車突圍衝入尖沙嘴警署脫身，因頭面受傷，右眼瘀黑，需往醫院治理。<br />\n<br />\n至前年2月，屯門良景市集在大年初二發生毆鬥事件。據悉，肥威被指有份在場「坐鎮」，疑監察及指揮多名有背景「管理員」，驅趕疑有黑幫「新義安」撐腰的小販，雙方最後爆發衝突。<br />\n<br />\n■記者梁曙光  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n「熱心巿民」現場主動爆相爆片<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n水鬼隊落海蒐證<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「熱心巿民」現場主動爆相爆片<br />\n<br />\n水鬼隊落海蒐證<br />\n<br />\n七煞斬債仔　反遭30人打爆缸收錯風撞正「大佬」賀壽人強馬壯冇得走"},{"pid":"fb3ee8362f69193bb180ded06b0aa669bcbb9cee","tid":678247,"uid":86756,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T02:41:23.000Z","msg":"沙田me"},{"pid":"3d87355f405c65bb077848ccfe0f5b6986e5ae64","tid":678247,"uid":59283,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fb3ee8362f69193bb180ded06b0aa669bcbb9cee","tid":678247,"uid":86756,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T02:41:23.000Z","msg":"沙田me"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T02:47:48.000Z","msg":"油麻they"},{"pid":"99306382fc0eeeb5412587424e0ec1a296236391","tid":678247,"uid":39439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T02:49:18.000Z","msg":"姓黃叫Ken <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2d7404dc522d836ebf8e680acece51dcb67c15f","tid":678247,"uid":177219,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T02:54:10.000Z","msg":"今次唔係食物名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33c1c58aeed5614392dd0a618a7b3d2fe1fffa8c","tid":678247,"uid":26553,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T03:51:28.000Z","msg":"良景之亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n應該要同黃巾之亂一併寫入史記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有水房大佬要突圍入差館避<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n玩gta咁撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81cc99647928fbdc004fe66626c8cfe1